-Try this.

595
00:42:26,291 --> 00:42:28,625
-Try it.
-Puek, go on.

596
00:42:29,125 --> 00:42:31,791
-Just try it.
-Eat up.

597
00:42:31,875 --> 00:42:32,875
-Right. Just try it.
-Eat up.

598
00:42:44,958 --> 00:42:47,458
