606
00:43:35,083 --> 00:43:36,125
How was it?

607
00:43:38,000 --> 00:43:39,708
Damn good!

608
00:43:42,208 --> 00:43:44,666
My Nak is the best cook.

609
00:43:45,208 --> 00:43:47,541
