741
00:50:03,125 --> 00:50:06,333
It means "mind your own business."
Did you have to ask?

742
00:50:06,416 --> 00:50:08,416
Just go!

743
00:50:20,166 --> 00:50:22,208
Damn, I think Nak is on to us now.

744
00:50:23,791 --> 00:50:25,291
